profile: It would be fair to say I am a paint geek.  I have been painting things for as long as I can remember.  I began my professional painting career back in 1999.  I have taken a couple detours over the years but have always come back to what I realized was a true passion in my life.  I understand the importance of value and customer experience.  I conduct my business professionally and with integrity.  Delivering quality residential painting services.  Specializing in cabinet finishing and refinishing.  Owned and operated by Curt Lander, a Journeyman Painter/Decorator dedicated to the art and science of residential coatings for over 20 years.
services: Residential interior painting services and fine sprayed finishes.  Hand staining and varnishing.
brands: Sherwin-Williams, Benjamin Moore, Cloverdale Paint, Dulux, Envirolak wood coatings
specialities: Kitchen and bathroom cabinet repainting.  Fine sprayed finishes.
name: CCPI Interior Finishing
